metadata.name: First breath
metadata.description:
/first breath/ 

Meditations on the rents in the fabric of time - the moments that slip through unlived, the pauses we forget to take, the periods we don't remember. 

Process: 
Sketches are created using outputs of a GAN trained on the artistâ€™s paintings and are then fed into DALL.E to create iterations that are printed, cut, and used to create new pieces through collages. As a final step, these collages are scanned and imported into Procreate to be painted over by the artist.
